law.history: Repealed 1949 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 11, sec. 13. -- Created 1948 Ky. Acts ch. 237, sec. 8, effective March 25, 1948.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Powers of commission with respect to purchase, lease or sale of real estate -- Allocation of cost of land and building projects -- Title to real estate when revenue bonds issued, lease agreements -- Eminent domain -- Lease of state lands and buildings to private interests.
